quran[8{c,v,t}:
3,101,tumahray liye kufar ki taraf jaane ka ab kya mauqa baqi hai jab ke tum ko Allah ki ayaat sunai ja rahi hain aur tumahray darmain is kaRasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam mojood hai? jo Allah ka daman mazbooti ke sath thaamay ga woh zaroor raah raast paley ga
3,102,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, Allah se daro jaissa ke is se darny ka haq hai tum ko mout nah aeye magar is haal mein ke tum muslim ho"
3,103,"sab mil kar Allah ki rassi ko mazboot pakar lau aur tafarruqa mein nah parro Allah ke uss ahsaan ko yaad rakho jo is ne tum par kya hai tum aik dosray ke dushman thay, uss ne tumahray dil joor diye aur is ke fazl o karam se tum bhai bhai ban gay tum aag se bharay hue aik garhay ke kinare kharray thay, Allah ne tum ko is se bacha liya is terhan Allah apni nishanain tumahray samnay roshan karta hai shayad ke inn alamton se tumhe apni Falah ka seedha rasta nazar aa jaye"
3,104,"tum mein kuch log to aisay zaroor hi rehne chahaiyn jo neki ki taraf bulayen, bhalai ka hukum den, aur buraiyon se roktay rahen jo log yeh kaam karen ge wohi Falah payen ge"
3,105,kahin tum unn logon ki terhan nah ho jana jo firqoun mein Butt gay aur khuli khuli wazeh Hadayat panay ke baad phir ikhtilafat mein mubtala hue jinhon ne yeh rawish ikhtiyar ki woh uss roz sakhtsaza payen ge
3,106,"jabkay kuch log surkh ro hon ge aur kuch logon ka mun kala hoga, jin ka mun kala hoga ( un se kaha jaye ga ke ) Nemat imaan panay ke baad bhi tum ne kafirana rawayya ikhtiyar kya? acha to ab iss kufran Nemat ke sila mein azaab ka maza chako"
3,107,rahay woh log jin ke chehray roshan hon ge to unn ko Allah ke daman rehmat mein jagah miley gi aur hamesha woh isi haalat mein rahen ge
3,108,yeh Allah ke arshadat hain jo hum tumhe theek theek snarhe hain kyunkay Allah duniya walon par zulm karne ka koi iradah nahi rakhta
